'''Jordan Miller''' (born in [[New York, New York]]) is an [[United States|American]] [[figure skater]]. He is the 2006 US National Junior silver medalist, 2007 US National Senior competitor, and won the silver medal at the 2006 [[Ondrej Nepela Memorial]].<ref>[http://www.isufs.org/events/fsevent00009370.htm 2006 Ondrej Nepela Memorial]</ref> Miller also worked as a figure skating judge but has moved on to pursue a career in law and is currently studying at the University of Virginia School of Law.
